{"sn12.3:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.3 ","sn12.3:0.2":"1. Buddhavagga ","sn12.3:0.3":"Patipadasutta ","sn12.3:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati …pe… ","sn12.3:1.2":"“micchapatipadanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami sammapatipadanca. ","sn12.3:1.3":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","sn12.3:1.4":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.3:1.5":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.3:2.1":"“Katama ca, bhikkhave, micchapatipada? ","sn12.3:2.2":"Avijjapaccaya, bhikkhave, sankhara; ","sn12.3:2.3":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam …pe… ","sn12.3:2.4":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.3:2.5":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, micchapatipada. ","sn12.3:3.1":"Katama ca, bhikkhave, sammapatipada? ","sn12.3:3.2":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha sankharanirodho; ","sn12.3:3.3":"sankharanirodha vinnananirodho …pe… ","sn12.3:3.4":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.3:3.5":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, sammapatipada”ti. ","sn12.3:3.6":"Tatiyam. "}